# Pie in the Sky - Project Context

## Project Overview
This is a Hugo static site generator project for "Pie in the Sky in Eden" - a pie business website run by Kelli in Eden, Utah. The site showcases various types of pies including fruit pies, cream pies, specialty pies, dinner pies, and hand pies.

## Technology Stack
- **Framework**: Hugo (Go-based static site generator)
- **Styling**: SCSS (compiled to CSS)
- **UI Framework**: Bootstrap
- **JavaScript**: jQuery
- **Icons**: Font Awesome, Themify Icons
- **Plugins**: Slick (carousels), Google Maps API
- **Deployment**: Netlify (configured via netlify.toml)

## Project Structure
- `config.toml`: Main Hugo configuration file with site settings, navigation, params, and styling
- `content/`: Content files organized by category:
  - `fruit-pies/`: Seasonal fruit pie listings
  - `cream-pies/`: Year-round cream pie listings
  - `special-pies/`: Specialty pie listings (holiday/seasonal)
  - `dinner-pies/`: Savory dinner pie listings
  - `hand-pies/`: Hand pie listings (sweet and savory)
  - `blog/`: Blog posts
  - `contact/`: Contact page
  - `faq/`: FAQ page
- `data/`: YAML data files:
  - `homepage.yml`: Homepage content configuration
  - `contact.yml`: Contact information
  - `faq.yml`: FAQ data
- `layouts/`: Hugo template files:
  - `_default/`: Base templates (baseof.html, list.html, single.html)
  - `index.html`: Homepage template
  - `partials/`: Reusable template partials (header, footer, seasonal, etc.)
- `assets/`: Source assets:
  - `scss/`: SCSS source files
  - `js/`: JavaScript source files
  - `plugins/`: Third-party plugin files
- `static/`: Static files served directly (images, compiled assets)
- `public/`: Generated static site output (gitignored, generated by Hugo)

## Key Features
- Seasonal content sections (Thanksgiving, Christmas, etc.) with configurable gradients
- Product category sections with pricing and descriptions
- Contact form integration
- Google Maps integration for location
- Venmo payment integration
- Responsive design using Bootstrap grid system
- Custom SCSS styling with configurable color scheme

## Development Workflow
- Run `hugo server` or use `devel.sh` for local development
- Hugo watches for changes and regenerates the site
- SCSS is compiled during the build process
- Site is deployed to Netlify

## Important Configuration Notes
- Base URL: https://pieinthesky-eden.com
- Primary color: #C6600D (orange/brown pie theme)
- Contact: order@pieinthesky-eden.com, 801-941-1855
- Location: Eden, UT
- Seasonal gradients can be configured in config.toml (params.style.gradient)

## Content Management
- Product listings are managed in `content/` directories
- Homepage sections are configured in `data/homepage.yml`
- Navigation menu is configured in `config.toml` under `[menu.main]`
- Each pie category has its own section with enable/disable flags in homepage.yml

## Styling Guidelines
- Primary color: #C6600D
- Text colors: #333333 (light), #222222 (dark)
- Uses Bootstrap classes for layout and components
- Custom SCSS in `assets/scss/` for theme-specific styling
- Seasonal themes can be applied via gradient configuration

